https://www.tatvic.com/privacy-policy/?ref=plugin_policy&utm_source=plugin_backend&utm_medium=magento2_free_extension&utm_campaign=GDPR_complaince_ecomm_plugins">privacy policy</a>.]]>
                   </comment>
